      • getConfigurationValue

        static String getConfigurationValue​(Configuration configuration,
                                    String fieldName,
                                    String defaultValue)
        Get value for the field name from the configuration. If it is blank or null, then return the default value.
        Parameters:
        configuration - Configuration to look up field name from
        fieldName - String of the field name to look for
        defaultValue - String for the default value to use
        Returns:
        value for field name or default value if field not found
